N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 6 ยง 105.3 - General provisions

State Regulations
(a) Users
of the area must comply with all regulatory signs posted by the
department. (b) The department may
eject any person from the area for behavior that endangers the general safety
of persons using the area or interferes with the management and use of the
area's natural resources. Notes
